{"tid":1560221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"離清算警察近了，前線阿sir準備好出賣大sir未？","createTime":"2019-09-11T06:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T03:40:44.000Z","uid":222970,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6a47967c7ff2c25f8151205cb00cdedfe6c9eb50","tid":1560221,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"比我係警察，係依一刻我仲唔收集哂所有證據，仲要大大力支持成立獨立調查委員會。個乜鬼委員會咪又係只會查大粒唔查細嘅，個會查到幾千人咩？睇鉛水嗰次就知，42樓膠層咪又係只會射比啲細嘅食。所以一定要 keep 好哂啲對話同命令，拉啲膠層落馬。空左啲位出來邊個上位唔洗我教下話？<br />\n<br />\n有功就大sir拎<br />\n鑊就你地前線咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n清算黎啦 為左自保 你地知點做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d807a9a23d567ad052302d1c723102110f2dfb1","tid":1560221,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:24:28.000Z","msg":"就算唔出賣<br />\n<br />\nkeep起上頭動員證據，保平安"},{"pid":"d4160974cc4092a5cd4e0ca327af5c89fcd85cde","tid":1560221,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"支持阿sir自己走唔甩都唔好比大嘅走甩"},{"pid":"41c8609b9727b30cebb1af4e54561c2959d64734","tid":1560221,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:25:43.000Z","msg":"大sir都可以出賣大sir<br />\n少個人同自己爭上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8d01daee5d7919b87ccb5c6026bf2087cbfb21","tid":1560221,"uid":278990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"睇落好撚似...<br />\n做過衰野既記住點自保"},{"pid":"59518112a210e59c0180c6192f07415fd1cf46b3","tid":1560221,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:32:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Keep證據 保平安 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"2b703adf5aa6d3a741b922ee58283aa9b96bcc25","tid":1560221,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited